OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with plenty of clear
OL,7,Fperiods. Cloud will gradually increase
OL,8,Ffrom the north overnight, perhaps
OL,9,Fbringing the odd spot of drizzle
OL,10,Flater. Staying quite warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA bright start to Saturday
OL,13,Fwith lengthy sunshine, though cloud is
OL,14,Fset to increase from the north into
OL,15,Fthe afternoon, with some showery rain
OL,16,Fdeveloping. Still warm, though rather
OL,17,Fbreezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
